76
00:04:26.860 --> 00:04:30.520
On behalf of my core investigators, it is my

77
00:04:30.540 --> 00:04:34.260
pleasure to present telatrexib in TKI-naive

78
00:04:34.360 --> 00:04:38.120
patients with ROS1 rearranged non-small cell lung cancer:

79
00:04:38.760 --> 00:04:42.600
updated data from TRUST-1 and TRUST-2 trials.

80
00:04:43.660 --> 00:04:44.880
Here are my disclosures.

81
00:04:46.420 --> 00:04:50.060
Telatrexib is a next generation CNS active

82
00:04:50.480 --> 00:04:54.280
selective ROS TKI, which is currently approved in the United

83
00:04:54.360 --> 00:04:58.160
States, Japan, and China for the treatment of patients

84
00:04:58.560 --> 00:05:02.460
with locally advanced metastatic ROS1 rearranged non-small cell

85
00:05:02.500 --> 00:05:03.160
lung cancer.

86
00:05:04.180 --> 00:05:07.420
We know that telatrexib has shown robust efficacy,

87
00:05:07.860 --> 00:05:11.660
including intracranial efficacy and manageable safety

88
00:05:11.720 --> 00:05:15.520
profile in both TKI-naive and TKI pre-treated

89
00:05:15.620 --> 00:05:19.580
patients based on the Phase II TRUST-1 and TRUST-2

90
00:05:19.720 --> 00:05:20.220
trials.

91
00:05:21.380 --> 00:05:25.120
Here, we report updated efficacy analysis for telatrexib

92
00:05:25.580 --> 00:05:29.080
in TKI-naive patients from TRUST-1 and TRUST-2 trials,

93
00:05:29.620 --> 00:05:33.570
together with updated safety data from an integrated

94
00:05:33.820 --> 00:05:34.820
safety analysis.

95
00:05:36.260 --> 00:05:37.560
Here is the study designs.

96
00:05:38.460 --> 00:05:42.300
TRUST-1 and TRUST-2 trials were a pivotal Phase II trials,

97
00:05:42.800 --> 00:05:46.600
which enrolled patients with locally advanced or metastatic non-small cell

98
00:05:46.610 --> 00:05:50.400
lung cancer with ROS1 fusion, performance status of zero to

99
00:05:50.500 --> 00:05:50.780
one.

100
00:05:51.580 --> 00:05:55.500
Brain metastasis were allowed if stable.

101
00:05:55.560 --> 00:05:58.420
TRUST-1 enrolled primarily in China.

102
00:05:59.120 --> 00:06:02.560
TRUST-2 was a global study enrolling in North

103
00:06:02.680 --> 00:06:04.800
America, Europe, and Asia

104
00:06:04.900 --> 00:06:08.584
Pacific.I'm going to concentrate on cohort

105
00:06:08.724 --> 00:06:12.544
one in both of those studies, which treated patients who

106
00:06:12.564 --> 00:06:16.444
were ROS1 TKI naive. Patient received telatrexib

107
00:06:16.764 --> 00:06:18.524
six hundred milligrams once a day.

108
00:06:19.284 --> 00:06:23.264
Primary endpoint was IRC assessed confirmed

109
00:06:23.364 --> 00:06:26.524
overall response rate per RECIST one point one.

110
00:06:27.224 --> 00:06:30.334
Key secondary endpoints were duration of response,

111
00:06:30.864 --> 00:06:34.624
PFS, OS, intracranial overall response

112
00:06:34.704 --> 00:06:36.104
rate, and safety.

113
00:06:37.224 --> 00:06:41.024
The efficacy population that I'm reporting includes TKI

114
00:06:41.084 --> 00:06:44.884
naive patients in TRUST-1 and TRUST-2 trial with at least

115
00:06:45.004 --> 00:06:48.724
one measurable disease who received telatrexib at six hundred

116
00:06:48.824 --> 00:06:50.004
milligrams once a day.

117
00:06:50.844 --> 00:06:54.584
Safety population includes both TKI naive and TKI

118
00:06:54.664 --> 00:06:58.464
pre-treated patients from phase one and phase two trials

119
00:06:58.824 --> 00:07:01.304
who received at least one dose of telatrexib.

120
00:07:02.464 --> 00:07:03.604
Here are the demographics.

121
00:07:04.404 --> 00:07:07.984
Demographics for this patient population is as expected for

122
00:07:08.004 --> 00:07:11.364
ROS1 rearranged non-small cell lung cancer with high

123
00:07:11.463 --> 00:07:15.304
proportion of never smokers. Majority of the patients had

124
00:07:15.384 --> 00:07:18.704
stage four disease and performance status of one.

125
00:07:19.744 --> 00:07:23.304
Very important to highlight, if you look at the pooled efficacy

126
00:07:23.364 --> 00:07:26.684
population of one hundred fifty-seven patients, that

127
00:07:26.844 --> 00:07:30.684
nineteen percent of the patients received prior chemotherapy and

128
00:07:30.744 --> 00:07:34.484
twenty-three point six percent of the patients had brain metastasis.

129
00:07:35.944 --> 00:07:39.804
Here is the efficacy data. Confirmed overall response rate

