00:07:39.924 --> 00:07:43.664
in TRUST-1 trial was ninety point three percent.

131
00:07:44.304 --> 00:07:48.004
In patients who received prior chemotherapy, eighty-five point zero.

132
00:07:48.564 --> 00:07:52.364
TRUST-2 confirmed overall response rate eighty-eight point

133
00:07:52.524 --> 00:07:56.284
nine percent and prior chemotherapy hundred percent.

134
00:07:56.344 --> 00:07:59.764
In pooled efficacy analysis of one hundred fifty-seven patients,

135
00:08:00.284 --> 00:08:04.244
confirmed overall response rate was eighty-nine point eight, and in

136
00:08:04.284 --> 00:08:06.964
patients who received prior chemotherapy, it was ninety.

137
00:08:07.724 --> 00:08:11.604
Very important to highlight intracranial efficacy of

138
00:08:11.664 --> 00:08:15.504
the telatrexib. Intracranial confirmed overall response

139
00:08:15.564 --> 00:08:18.564
rate was eighty-seven point five percent in TRUST-1,

140
00:08:19.304 --> 00:08:23.124
sixty-six point seven in TRUST-2, and seventy-six point

141
00:08:23.244 --> 00:08:27.224
five in pooled analysis. Waterfall plot are presented

142
00:08:27.304 --> 00:08:31.044
for you to review. Patients with brain metastasis are

143
00:08:31.124 --> 00:08:33.304
indicated here with green dots.

144
00:08:35.264 --> 00:08:39.164
Duration of response. In pooled efficacy population of one

145
00:08:39.244 --> 00:08:42.584
hundred forty-one patients and median follow-up of

