00:08:42.985 --> 00:08:46.524
thirty-five point five months, median duration of response

147
00:08:46.864 --> 00:08:50.644
was forty-nine point seven months with lower bound of confidence

148
00:08:50.704 --> 00:08:54.584
interval of thirty-eight months and high bound of confidence interval

149
00:08:54.624 --> 00:08:58.414
not reached. At four years, fifty-three point four

150
00:08:58.484 --> 00:09:01.844
percent of responding patients were still responding.

151
00:09:03.204 --> 00:09:05.724
Same data separated by each trial.

152
00:09:05.804 --> 00:09:09.744
TRUST-1, median follow-up of fifty-one month, median duration of

