168
00:10:02.084 --> 00:10:05.584
Same data separated by the trial. In TRUST-1,

169
00:10:05.804 --> 00:10:09.284
median PFS of forty-nine point six months.

170
00:10:09.344 --> 00:10:12.924
At four years, fifty point nine percent of the patients were still without

171
00:10:12.964 --> 00:10:13.484
progression.

172
00:10:14.304 --> 00:10:17.584
TRUST-2, median progression-free survival was not

173
00:10:17.684 --> 00:10:20.784
