174
00:10:20.864 --> 00:10:24.843
months. At three years, fifty-five point nine percent

175
00:10:24.924 --> 00:10:27.284
of the patients were still without progression.

176
00:10:29.044 --> 00:10:32.284
Overall survival in TKI naive patients have not been reached.

177
00:10:32.844 --> 00:10:36.724
The lower bound of confidence interval is forty-seven point eight months.

178
00:10:37.424 --> 00:10:41.104
At four years, fifty-eight point four percent of patients were

179
00:10:41.204 --> 00:10:41.984
