212
00:12:37.128 --> 00:12:40.628
In conclusion, with three years of follow-up in pooled analysis

213
00:12:41.208 --> 00:12:44.478
and four years of follow-up in TRUST-1, telatrexate

214
00:12:44.728 --> 00:12:48.568
demonstrates high endurable response rate in TKI-naive patients

215
00:12:49.068 --> 00:12:52.808
with ROS rearranged non-small cell lung cancer with median duration of

216
00:12:52.868 --> 00:12:54.788
response exceeding four years.

217
00:12:55.968 --> 00:12:59.808
To the best of our knowledge, this represents the highest overall response

218
00:12:59.868 --> 00:13:03.388
