219
00:13:04.028 --> 00:13:08.008
reported to date for an FDA-approved ROS1 TKI in this

220
00:13:08.028 --> 00:13:09.128
patient populations.

221
00:13:10.028 --> 00:13:13.708
This presentation adds 10 months of additional follow-up

222
00:13:14.128 --> 00:13:18.108
since the last report, and telatrexate continues to demonstrate

223
00:13:18.408 --> 00:13:22.148
